-- Visteon to sell most of its auto interiors business to Cerberus
-- By Sagarika Jaisinghani in Bangalore
-- Fri May 02, 2014 07:10AM EDT
-- None



May 2 (Reuters) - Auto parts maker Visteon Corp <VC.N> said it would sell a majority of its automotive interiors business to private equity firm Cerberus Capital Management LP [CBC.UL].

The sale price was not disclosed. [ID:nPreqQvxya]